title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 10 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 10 2022
description:
The Bidas Touch: We have the highest inflation rate in 40 years. Very few people think Biden is doing a good job, even Dem approval rates are down. Snarky Psaki struggles to deal with Dems sounding like C&B. Buck's Fox News insightful opinion column on the crime tsunami that is the actual legacy of BLM. What's the Biden move now? Clay sums up where Biden is right now: "This is about as bad as it can possibly get, right? It is an unmitigated disaster right now for Joe Biden."
